  "prompt": "Should I text my crush first?",
  "response": "That's a personal decision, but here are some things to consider:\n\n1. Pros of texting first:\n- Shows confidence\n- Demonstrates you're interested\n- Can break the ice\n- Potentially starts a conversation\n\n2. Cons of texting first:\n- Might feel nervous\n- Could worry about seeming too eager\n- Unsure of their response\n\n3. Tips if you decide to text:\n- Keep it casual and light\n- Ask an open-ended question\n- Be yourself\n- Don't overthink it\n\nUltimately, if you're interested, taking a chance can be worth it. The worst that can happen is they don't respond enthusiastically.",
